description: emolition of the existing two-storey Jaguar showroom. Erection of a part two to part six storey L-shaped building fronting Roffey Street and adjacent 98-110 East Ferry Road; and erection of a part five to part seventeen storey building fronting Limeharbour, with a maximum height of 53m. Total of 213 residential units and 4 commercial units together with amenity area, landscaping, car parking and a public footpath.
